#: ../../F/flatten.rst:5
msgid "flatten"
msgstr "flatten"

#: ../../F/flatten.rst:7
msgid "vt\\."
msgstr "他動詞"

#: ../../F/flatten.rst:9
msgid ""
"[common] To remove structural information, esp. to filter something with an "
"implicit tree structure into a simple sequence of leaves; also tends to "
"imply mapping to :ref:`flat-ASCII`\\. \"This code flattens an expression "
"with parentheses into an equivalent :ref:`canonical` form.\""
msgstr ""
"[一般的]構造的な情報を取り除くこと。とりわけ、暗黙の木構造を持つ何かを、葉の単純な並びへとフィルタリングすること。\\ :ref:`flat-"
"ASCII`\\ へのマッピングを含意する傾向もある。「このコードは、括弧つきの式を等価な\\ :ref:`canonical`\\ "
"な形へとflattenする」。"
